simpleText: मे इसलिए बोलता हु इंडिया मे लोग देश भक्ति नही है तो लोगो को मिर्ची लगता है धर्म भक्त, जाति भक्त, पार्टी भक्त है  , 2014 से पहले निर्भया कांड हुआ था पुरा इंडिया का न्यूज़ चैनल और जनता सरक पे आंदोलन कर रही थी उसी वजह से मनमोहन सिंह का सरकार चला गया, अच्छी बात है लेकिन 2014 मे फिर मोदी जी आये 2014 से अब तक लाखों गिर्ल ,महिला, बालातकार हुआ है 1 साल के बच्ची से लेकर 60 साल के दादी तक का निर्भया कांड से भी खराब तरीके से हुआ है कश्मीर मे 8 साल के आसिफ के साथ 4 लोग 7 दिन तक मंदीर के पुजारी के रूम मे बंधक बना के रात दिन पुजारी और उसके साथी बालातकार किया जब दिल भर गया पथर से सर कुच के फेक दिया जंगल मे मजे की बात देखो बलतकरियो के समर्थन मे हजारो हिंदू संगठन के लोगो ने धरना प्रदर्शन किया, उतर प्रदेश मे बीजेपी नेता एक दलित की बेटी के साथ बालातकार किया जब उसके खिलाफ लरकी थाने मे गई तो बीजेपी नेता ने उस लरकी के पूरे परिवार को मरवा दिया, फिर लरकी को बालातकार किया जब लरकी मर गई तो पुलिस सबूत मिटाने के लिए उसके लास को जंगल मे लेके गई पेट्रोल और कुरा डाल के खुद जलाया, गुजरात मे बिलगिश बानो के 17 बलतकरियो को बीजेपी नेता उसके लोगो ने जेल से बाहर आने के बाद फूल माला से सोवागत किया गया, ये तो मेने एक दो उदाहरण दिया ऐसा 10 साल मे लाखों हुआ है अगर इंडिया के जनता सच मे बलतकरियो को सजा दिलाना चाहती तो निर्भया कांड के बाद चुप नाही बैठ जाति सब बलतकरि के खिलाफ आवाज उठती सजा दिलाती लेकिन ऐसा नही है अगर बालातकार  करने वाला उसके जाति या धर्म या राजनेतिक पार्टी का होता है तो मुह बंद कर लेता है, सिर्फ लोग सता परीवारतन के लिए बालातकार का मुद्दा उठाते है जैसे उनके मतलब के उनके लोगो का सता आता है तो उसके बाद बालातकार कितना भी हो कुछ नही बोले गे उल्टा उनके पार्टी या जाति या धर्म का निकल जाए तो उसको बचाने के लिए सारे साबुत मिटाने लगे गे और लरकी को ही गलत साबित करे गे, ये है हमारे इंडिया के लोगो का मानसिकता, जब मोदी सरकार 2014 मे आया जनता उसी वख्त चुप नही बैठ जाती कानून सख्त बनाने के लिए आंदोलन करती कानून सख्त हो जाता अच्छा से जांच होता जो दोसी होता उसको सजा मिलता सिर्फ मौत का और फासी होने लगती सारे बालातकार करने वाले को तो आज ये कोलकाता मे डॉक्टर का बालातकार नही होता, उतर प्रदेश के बनारस उनवर्सिटि मे बीजेपी it सेल के 3 लरको ने एक लरकी को बालातकार किया फिर 3 महिना तक लरकी भटकती रही है और उतर प्रदेश का योगी आदित्यनाथ उसको बचाने मे लगे थे पुलिस केस नही दर्ज कर रही थी, और बीजेपी it सेल के 3  बालातकारी मध्प्रदेश मे बीजेपी के लिए परचार कर रहे थे, बालातकार पे सिर्फ इंडिया मे राजनेतिक होता है और कुछ नही आज बंगाल मे ममता बनर्जी हार जाए उसके जगह बीजेपी आजाये तो कितना भी बालातकार होगा किसी भी लोगो का मुह नही खुले गा क्यू की उनको बालातकार से भरस्टाचार से दिकट नही है सिर्फ सता मे उनके लोग होना चाहिए, अगर लोगो को सच मे बालातकार से दिकत होता तो निर्भया कांड के बाद सो नही जाते, आसिफ, उन्नाव दलित बेटी सब के लिए आवाज उठाते, लोगो के अंडर जाति, धर्म, पार्टी का नसा कूट कूट के भरा है, बात सच है इसलिए बहुत लोगो को करवी लगे गी jay hind ( फैयाज़ अंसारी  )

simpleText: Bro you are a revolution.  I salute the way you are able to think about the extraordinary and bring out the real deal of what actually needs to be heard.  Everyone is protesting, "we want justice, we want justice". But no one is even trying to understand the root causes of such matters. And I really admire how you did your deep analytical and case based studies as always and bring out your solutions which according to me, are gems. You pointed out even the minor things that needs to be CHANGED by every INDIVIDUAL in this country. Everyone needs to understand the dire need of the situation. Govt, society, entertainment industry all the way to every single individual. Everyone needs to take ACTION on daily basis. I am myself a student and ngl my friends, my juniors, my seniors, all of us girls are having question mark on our existence!  We even shared how we cried whenever we listened to all these news of sexual abuses happening everyday.  All in all, you did a very good job. I really appreciate your courage to be different, to voice your own true opinions without any filter. And trust me, you got the best of opinions and solutions. Thank you a lott like seriously. Thankss✨✨

simpleText: सत्य की राह पर, जो चलता रहा, ध्रुव राठी वो नाम है, जिसने सच कहा। शिक्षा की बातें, जो उसने बताईं, अंधेरों में रोशनी की ज्योत जलाई।  वीडियो में उसने, जो सच दिखाया, सच की सदा, सदा से गहराई। निडरता से सच का जो साथ दिया, सत्य के पथ पर, सच्चे विचार लिए।  गलत को गलत, सही को सही कहा, दुनिया के सामने हर पर्दा उठाया। जिन्हें थी ज़रूरत, उन्होंने पाया प्रकाश, ध्रुव ने बांटा, हर घर में ज्ञान का प्रकाश।  साहस से वो हर जुल्म के खिलाफ खड़ा, शिक्षा और जागरूकता का दिया वो बढ़ा। ध्रुव राठी का ये सफर यूं ही चले, सच्चाई के साथ, उसकी हर बात जले।  जो सीखना चाहें, वो उससे सीखें, ध्रुव के साथ चलें, और सच्चाई देखें। ध्रुव राठी, तुमको सलाम हमारा, सच की मशाल, तुम ही हो हमारा।

simpleText: Sad true story— Rapes are often caused by blood related relatives and this is increasing day by day in a heinous scale. My girlfriend was raped severly by her cousin brothers when she was only 11 years old. As she was lived in a joint family,this heinous act went for a long period of time.She was unconscious of the incident that was happening with him. Those do'gs presented it to her like a merry play or game! She suffered a lot,but couldn't tell her parents. The only person whom she gathered courage to say to was "Me". I was unknown of this fact.After nearly one year of relationship,she expresses her nightmares. I was totally shattered and heartbroken.  She was only 11! Only 11?!😅 What she went through was unbearable,I couldn't even think of. Yet,she was innocent,having no urge. Her relatives took her innocence ans abused her deeply. She realized everything when she was grown up at the age of 17! After that,she went to severe trauma and depression. She could't sleep at night for long time. Overthinking grabbed her deeply.  I supported her till then.Also,counseled her like her own parents. I loved her more than anyone in this world. I gave her my life's 4 years. She was my everything.  Cut to now,she is no more with me. She comitted suicide this year. The reason was not discovered! I thought she fully recovered from her trauma and all stuffs. I was astonished, what the reason was still unknown. Either this,or anything else,that she didn't share with me.  But she is no longer with me.I am totally broken.I couldn't think of anyone else except her. She could have a great life ahead.She could become happy and successful. She killed herself and lost every happiness,killed my happiness too. I couldn't give her justice too. If she was alive,I would have gave her justice.But she is dead now.  She faced only trauma in this world,nothing else.She could have give herself a chance to live life to the fullest. But alas!😅 May she rest in heaven. I love you my love!😄 Wish you came back and live with me again.  "RELATIVES ARE DANGEROUS,EVIL,HAVAN." "REALTIVES R@-PE OWN BLOOD." "DON'T R@PE, Let GIRLS LIVE their life PEACEFULLY with full FREEDOM.not TRAUMA, PLEASE"🙃

simpleText: My genuine opinion:   Everything changes with the perspective. The view on what we see ,narrates us the story that way and finally we get a conclusion. The so called term "moral values" changes its meaning. And we think we are right. And our mind is like "I am right that's it. I don't want anyone teach me. "   For example....   When watching reels I came across a video....   "A lady was going to dip ps 5 of his husband knowing that it is the only income sources but still she dips it telling him that he did not give her time and he always goes through his ps5. "   Now after watching that kind of reels the first thing comes to mind is ....   "RA*ISTS ARE NOT THAT BAD"  "RA*E HER"...... etc..   Now why does that come to my mind...  The reasons are.....    1. We are not godly beings.. Who don't even flicker in their worst time and do those things that should be done disrupting all kind of emotions.    2. Human brains " Moral Value" alter with every perspective with every angle of view, circumstances.    3.(Specific Point) When I saw that reel that idea came to my mind because I am flustered of all these things that women get extra opportunity in every field than men. In that case the reel is just a spark to the devastating fire. As I saw the video I did not think anything else. I just thought...   "How did she dare to dip the ps 5 in the pool"  "What if the roles are reversed"  "What kind of suppliment will he get now. He can't apply a case on her. If he did so he will got a divorce.. And the wife will  get an alimony... Which is husband's loss "  "What is the husband's mental state now... How upset he is.. "   That's the ingredients that made me think those lines I mentioned at the top....    So the main thing is the question you asked "kya rape galat hai " Changes with the angle of view...    May everyone can't say that thinking that society could spot him as a pshycho but that's the true thing that passes in his mind at such perspectives.    Hope @dhruvrathee read the whole comment of me... And give me a serious reply about my series of thoughts.   😶

simpleText: The idea that boys or men are negatively affected by girls or women wearing short clothes is a harmful stereotype that can perpetuate damaging attitudes and behaviors. Here's the truth:  1. Wearing short clothes is a personal choice, and girls and women have the right to decide how they want to dress. 2. Boys and men are capable of controlling their thoughts, feelings, and actions. They can respect others' boundaries and choices, regardless of clothing. 3. Objectifying or harassing someone based on their clothing is never acceptable. It's essential to promote respect, consent, and healthy relationships. 4. Let's focus on teaching boys and men about respect, boundaries, and healthy attitudes towards others, rather than blaming girls' and women's clothing choices.  Remember, it's about promoting a culture of respect, understanding, and consent!❤

simpleText: ഒരു സ്ത്രീയെ നമ്മൾ വെറുക്കുന്നതിനാൽ ബലാത്സംഗം ചെയ്യണമെന്ന് നമ്മൾ വിശ്വസിക്കുന്നുവെങ്കിൽ.  നമ്മുടെ അമ്മയെയും സഹോദരിയെയും ഭാര്യയെയും മകളെയും ബലാത്സംഗം ചെയ്യാൻ മറ്റുള്ളവർക്ക് ലൈസൻസ് നമ്മൾ നൽകുന്നു.  നിങ്ങൾ ഒരു സ്ത്രീയെ നഗ്നയായി കണ്ടാൽ, അവളെ വസ്ത്രം  അണിയിക്കുക.  നഗ്നത ലൈംഗികതയ്ക്കുള്ള സമ്മതമല്ല.  ലൈംഗിക ബന്ധത്തിനിടയിൽ ഒരു സ്ത്രീ നിർത്താൻ പറഞ്ഞാൽ നിർത്തണം, അല്ലാത്തപക്ഷം അത് ബലാത്സംഗമാണ്.  അങ്ങനെ ജനിച്ചതിനാൽ ഒരു സ്ത്രീക്ക് അവൾ ശപിക്കപ്പെട്ടവളായി തോന്നരുത്.  അങ്ങിനെ വന്നാൽ അത് മനുഷ്യരാശിയുടെ അന്ത്യം  കുറിക്കും.

simpleText: All valid points but this only covers one side of the crime. This type of crime is mostly reported as being done by men against women but that is not the only case, It happens the other way around as well. If you tip the scale in one direction it will lead to a new problem. If a woman initiates or starts teasing a man younger than her, should she be held accountable for harassment equally as a man would have been in a similar situation? If a gang of women rape a young man they should be punished equally by law. Do you think women don't tease and bully men whom they consider weaker than themselves? Having laws strict only for men will give certain women a chance to start abusing the system and blame innocent men at work for sexual harassment if they disagree with them or rejects their sexual advances. It all seems far fetched to an unaware person but is very much the reality. In future this will create distance between normal men and women, because women will be afraid of men harassing them and men will be afraid of women falsely accusing them of rape.

simpleText: India's biggest weakness is rampant Corruption and Chaos..and the biggest reason for the growth of all Corruptions and Crime is our country's lax.. stagnant.. biased.. Judiciary System based on British-era's crooked hermad Laws which is moved and directed by money ghouls unscrupulous Lawyers , self-righteous, shameless Judiciary ; being the most populous country in the world, such a law and justice system in INDIA is  nothing but anathema ; When people go to the door of the court to seek Justice for an unjust Crime, they first have to go to the money ghoul Lawyer. The torture of the court will start after the trial candidate's case starts.. The Court will be continuing sprinkling salt on their cut of  wounds.. giving date after date.. make them  waiting for the trial and final Judgement forever.. when will it the end, the naive trial candidate, the justice seeker does not know.. the case maybe pending for 10 - 20 - 30 years. .. or will continue longer, no one knows in this India ; The lamp of many Justice Seekers lives are extinguished, many have no more time to listen to the words of Judgment ; On the other hand, famous Criminals appoint expensive Lawyers, who are experts in the field of weaving a web of lies, who are always ready to find out the intricate immaginatory ways to prove their criminal Clients INNOCENT or reduce the sentence so that they can get Bail immediately ; As a result, Nowadays most of the crime prone people become extremely confident. .. The common man's trust in law and order is decreasing day by day.. which is slowly leading our country to Hell ; At this moment few Crores of cases are pending in different courts of the country.. which is a World record ; All small and big developed countries of the world are wrapped in strict rule of Law,  people of these countries are forced to follow all good  rules and regulations of a responsible citizen.. so when we walk on the streets of Dubai or Tokyo or London.. we are forced to think many times, should we throw a piece of small polythene or even a piece of cigarette butt on the street or not !! On the other hand, in our country people never hesitate to spit on the walls of government office stairs !! One example is enough to understand the whole difference between India  and advanced world.. as well as true law and order situation of this largest democracy .
